## Loop Template
```assembly
AND R1, R1, #0      ; counter = 0
LD R2, MAX          ; load limit
LOOP
    ; Loop body here
    ADD R1, R1, #1  ; increment counter
    NOT R3, R2
    ADD R3, R3, #1  ; R3 = -MAX
    ADD R3, R1, R3  ; counter - MAX
    BRn LOOP        ; continue if counter < MAX
